{"tid":2113690,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【支那神童殞落】3歲熟背數百首唐詩13歲入大學　神童1年後滿缸紅險遭退學","createTime":"2020-07-18T09:45:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T15:17:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3da5c36919365a47ccaa1a1a5a0a4d028dcdb837","tid":2113690,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"內地一名青年天資聰敏，小時候被喻為「神童」，13歲已跳級入大學，贏在起跑線上，卻後勁不繼，差點面臨退學。表面原因是他的獎學金被撤回，而撤回的決定涉及神童的讀書態度表現及個人品行，令曾備受觸目的一代神童殞落。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內地傳媒報道，1996年在貴州出生的廖葳，從小天資聰敏，3歲已經熟背幾百首唐詩，5歲提早讀小學，僅花2年半就完成6年小學課程，直接跳級讀高中，13歲時在高考取得563分佳績，可入讀中國農業大學。<br />\n<br />\n13時獲獎學金讀大學<br />\n廖葳家境不算富裕，父母擔心難以負擔兒子的大學學費和生活費。當時，貴州當地企業「貴州茅台公司」知道神童的情況，決定給廖葳獎學金，承諾支付4年大學全額學費及生活費，讓他專注讀書，不用憂愁經濟開支。<br />\n<br />\n當時，13歲的廖葳宣稱希望成為科學家，貢獻社會，並計劃花2年修畢本科學分、2年讀研究生、2年讀完博士等，充滿大志。<br />\n<br />\n入大學後沉迷打機成績差<br />\n不料，1年之後廖葳險被迫退學，原因是他不再獲發獎學金。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，貴州茅台突然決定停止資助神童，是基於廖葳上大學後沒有努力讀書，沉迷打機，常常走堂，成績差到每科目都不合格。成績差外，另一方有感神童從來沒有道謝該企業。<br />\n<br />\n最後廖葳不用退學，但被迫轉學系，一代神童就此殞落。外界紛紛討論雖然孩子資優跳級，但父母未有好好教導做人處事，令孩子過份以自我中心，爸媽有份摧毀神童。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2695000/2699514/talent_thumb_20200718_S_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2695000%2F2699514%2Ftalent_thumb_20200718_S_1024.jpg&h=07eb820b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07589b56094b94fd0597d4bb7fa18df1ac00fa8e","tid":2113690,"uid":42804,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:50:05.000Z","msg":"方仲永<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5eb57d8b7586c63c357b1d53618e715e50f66f","tid":2113690,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"大陸仔格，典型案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f161f0171a4de59d02e336ee29701d21fa63771b","tid":2113690,"uid":62532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"職業 ： 神童<br />\n收入 ： 廣告<br />\n員工福利 ： 免大學學費"},{"pid":"efe80f29ddbd443c5504348f1047de28fbb96957","tid":2113690,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"諗住做電競神童"},{"pid":"a35650c9f94b3bb834707f3a1cbd18fab46d5ece","tid":2113690,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"農業大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n調理農務都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e15721824e01520172ad9442055816441f43e1","tid":2113690,"uid":71237,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"因為愈高層次嘅教育就愈唔係靠背誦。<br />\n佢識背唐詩三百首同有能力讀大學根本差好遠。"},{"pid":"cc2f217a1c301813fcc6d6d1870ced65be9d328f","tid":2113690,"uid":359022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:08:47.000Z","msg":"小時了了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0922460531f4a1d4760aa6d2a76723ec91500c44","tid":2113690,"uid":335434,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"dd5eb57d8b7586c63c357b1d53618e715e50f66f","tid":2113690,"uid":105678,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"大陸仔格，典型案例<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:14:03.000Z","msg":"佢地由出世去到高考都係由老豆老母日日軍訓式監撚住讀書 <br />\n一入到大學無人督撚住仲唔即刻喪去玩同打機搵返自己嘅童年咩 <br />\n同埋 去外國留學果班仲多呢啲例子 有啲去到外國幾年用咗百鳩幾萬就係打足幾年機 直到走堂走到無埋個學生Visa先死返去鬼国 然後上淘寶買張假cert就話自己係「海歸派」呃飯食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a141338468d44fecb15017a1186d17b1ebaaea","tid":2113690,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"efe80f29ddbd443c5504348f1047de28fbb96957","tid":2113690,"uid":2230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:05:24.000Z","msg":"諗住做電競神童"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:19:24.000Z","msg":"家陣都24啦仲神咩童，廢青就有佢份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa1b17c353934e2f6c8094390b45869316120ff","tid":2113690,"uid":7138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:30:47.000Z","msg":"茅台賣廣告姐"},{"pid":"48a5ee75543360e66eaa58fda46436b111d41c89","tid":2113690,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:34:01.000Z","msg":"on9仔"},{"pid":"36b0df4d653d01c496474f1e9401b990709db9a6","tid":2113690,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:34:06.000Z","msg":"飲得免費茅台多，連個人都廢埋。"},{"pid":"06ba638d94002d7176ffe4c5ad5f890cd99db63f","tid":2113690,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a35650c9f94b3bb834707f3a1cbd18fab46d5ece","tid":2113690,"uid":122083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"農業大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n調理農務都唔撚識<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a80fbabc3ac4d4f602e52f5091199c13deefa49","tid":2113690,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"我記得08  <br />\n<br />\n香港又有個神童，入大學！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知佢家下點？"},{"pid":"d32fab49c332c2e850683874820e9a9c7208c5b3","tid":2113690,"uid":335434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4a80fbabc3ac4d4f602e52f5091199c13deefa49","tid":2113690,"uid":132810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"我記得08  <br />\n<br />\n香港又有個神童，入大學！！<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知佢家下點？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T12:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.math.ucla.edu/people/visiting/march\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=